    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## You as Creator. AI as Collaborator.\r\n\r\nIn this exercise, AI will act as a collaborator, giving you **suggestions** to improve your creative content.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Input the **creative content piece** you recorded in your activity guide into AI Chat.\r\n2. **Have AI evaluate** your content based on one of the following:\r\n    - **Clarity** (*Ask AI if it is easy to understand*)\r\n    - **Engagement** (*Ask AI if it captures interest*)\r\n    - **Originality** (*Ask AI if it feels unique*)\r\n3. **Prompt the AI** to provide a few suggestions for the **style, format or tone**\r\n    - _Note: **DO NOT ask AI to revise** the content for you—only ask for **ideas and suggestions**._\r\n4. **Revise your original piece** based on the feedback and any suggestions you want to implement from the AI and **record it in your Activity Guide**.\r\n    - *Note: it is fine if you don’t want to implement any of AI’s suggestions. Just make sure to note this in your activity guide and reasons why.*\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [**Struggling with creating your creative content?**]\r\nTry copy and pasting the following revised prompt into AI Chat: \r\nHere are some examples of what your creative content might look like:\r\n- **Write a futuristic advertisement for a self-driving bicycle.**\r\n    - _Example: The world’s first fully autonomous e-bicycle that takes you wherever you need to go! Built-in smart navigation, voice control, and auto-balance technology make every ride effortless._\r\n- **Write a short poem about a city in the year 2100.**\r\n    - _Example: Neon cities, skies so bright, Hover cars zoom through the night._\r\n- **1-2 sentence description for new video game concept that involves time travel.**\r\n    - _Example: In Time Slip, players control a scientist trapped in a glitching time loop, jumping between prehistoric jungles, futuristic cities, and medieval castles. Repair history before reality collapses!_\r\n- **Create a tagline for a movie about AI detectives.**\r\n    - _Example: They don’t just solve crimes… they predict them before they happen._\r\n- **Write a 2-3 sentence introduction to a science fiction novel.**\r\n    - _Example: The year is 2543*, and Earth is no longer home—humanity has fled to the plant Arid**-9**. But when an unknown signal emerges from Earth, whispering in a forgotten language, scientist Mira Voss must decide: Is it a warning… or an invitation?_\r\n\r\n:::",
